** Story Teller: The Art of the Story Book
------------------------------------------------------------


** The Works
------------------------------------------------------------

All month long!

“Story Tellers: The Art of the Storybook” is curated by a Central Ohio illustrator and freelance artist for The Walt Disney Company. The exhibit captures the technical, whimsical, and educational components of storytelling through illustration. Original illustrations by local, regional and nationally known artists provide a glimpse into their unique creative progression by sharing five themed areas of the design process with the audience. This process acts as the common thread for each artist to achieve their final artistic accomplishment; the story book. This exhibition will remain on display until October 11.

Event Website >> (http://www.attheworks.org/visit/calendar-event.aspx?id=79fe30c6-0a01-44af-8d8a-6b94cf0d813c)

