** Harvest Fair
------------------------------------------------------------


** Stratford Ecological Farm
------------------------------------------------------------

September 27th

One of Stratford's biggest events of the year: a celebration of Stratford and of down-home family fun. Family-centered in every way, the farm is transformed into a playground in celebration of the season. With a variety of entertainment on the picnic area stage, a kids world--an active location with kites, stilts, face painting and a giant earth ball--and a hay bale toddler area with farm toys, kids of all ages can discover their inner farmer by climbing on a tractor, making apple cider, riding on a horse drawn wagon, grinding grain and more. Stratford sells home-grown food for lunch and volunteers provide an array of baked goods for sale.

Event Website >> (http://www.stratfordecologicalcenter.org/programs_events/special_events.html)

